page_title: Plan to manage costs for Azure OpenAI Service
page_description: Learn how to plan for and manage costs for Azure OpenAI by using cost analysis in the Azure portal.
chunk_content: Export cost dataYou can also export your cost data to a storage account, which is helpful when you need others to do extra data analysis for costs. For example, a finance team can analyze the data using Excel or Power BI. You can export your costs on a daily, weekly, or monthly schedule and set a custom date range. We recommend exporting cost data as the way to retrieve cost datasets.
